=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80\", \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101215322-bf5cd27642fc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80\"]','[]','aaaa7101-1111-4111-8111-aaaaaaaa7101','bbbb7010-1111-4111-8111-bbbbbbbb7010','2026-03-23 04:11:28.845','2026-03-23 04:11:28.845'),('d42db5ef-25bc-4ed6-939f-a2fc0c789894','news',1,0,0,0,'/uploads/news/5.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"/uploads/team/4.jpeg\",\"/uploads/material/bakim.jpg\"]','[]',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-25 03:40:07.426','2026-03-25 03:41:11.608');
