 04:11:27.913'),('44441505-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-bbbb1505tr01','bbbb1505-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1505','Malzeme','[\"PVC (≤55°C)\", \"PP (>55°C)\", \"CTP (FRP) (>55°C)\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.918','2026-03-23 04:11:27.918'),('44441505-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1505en01','bbbb1505-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1505','Material (Main/Bypass)','[\"PVC (≤55°C)\", \"PP (>55°C)\", \"FRP/CTP (>55°C)\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.919','2026-03-23 04:11:27.919'),('44441505-cccc-4ccc-8ccc-bbbb1505de01','bbbb1505-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1505','Material (Haupt/Bypass)','[\"PVC (≤55°C)\", \"PP (>55°C)\", \"FRP/CTP (>55°C)\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.923','2026-03-23 04:11:27.923'),('44441506-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-bbbb1506tr01','bbbb1506-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1506','Nozul Tipi','[\"Kademeli Nozul\", \"Papatya Nozul\", \"RK Fıskiye\", \"İthal Kule Nozulu\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.929','2026-03-23 04:11:27.929'),('44441506-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1506en01','bbbb1506-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1506','Nozzle Type','[\"Stepped Nozzle\", \"Daisy Nozzle\", \"RK Sprinkler\", \"Imported Tower Nozzle\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.933','2026-03-23 04:11:27.933'),('44441506-cccc-4ccc-8ccc-bbbb1506de01','bbbb1506-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1506','Düsentyp','[\"Stufendüse\", \"Gänseblümchen-Düse\", \"RK Sprinkler\", \"Importierte Kühlturmdüse\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.937','2026-03-23 04:11:27.937'),('44441507-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-bbbb1507tr01','bbbb1507-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1507','Profil Kesiti','[\"I / U / L / Kutu (Box)\", \"Özel Kesim Boy\", \"Özel Kesit (talebe göre)\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.945','2026-03-23 04:11:27.945'),('44441507-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbb1507en01','bbbb1507-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1507','Profile Section','[\"I / U / L / Box\", \"Custom Cut Length\", \"Custom Section (on request)\"]','2026-03-23 04:11:27.947','2026-03-23 04:11:27.947'),('44441507-cccc-4ccc-8ccc-bbbb1507de01','bbbb1507-2222-4222-8222-bbbbbbbb1507','Profilquerschnitt','[\"I / U / L / Kasten (Box)\", \"Sonderlänge (Zuschnitt)\", \"Sonderquerschnitt (auf Anfrage)\"]','2026